  "dialogue": {
    "17": {
      "id": "17",
      "speaker": "Halsin",
      "text": "I received a dispatch from the grove. Life carries on there in our absence, just as nature intended.",
      "context": "NodeContext: thoughtful. A potentially dire crisis was averted",
      "checkflags": [
        "DEN_Lockdown_State_Active = False",
        "CURRENTREGION_CTY_Main_A",
        "ORI_Halsin_Event_RecievedGroveLetter = False"
      ],
      "setflags": [
        "ORI_Halsin_Event_RecievedGroveLetter"
      ],
      "ruletags": [],
      "approval": [],
      "rolls": "",
      "goto": "",
      "link": "21",
      "is_end": false,
      "node_type": "normal",
      "children": {
        "8": {
          "id": "8",
          "speaker": "Halsin",
          "text": "My chosen successor, Francesca, has proven to be a wise choice. Perhaps the wisest I ever made as Archdruid.",
          "context": "NodeContext: thoughtful. A potentially dire crisis was averted",
          "checkflags": [],
          "setflags": [],
          "ruletags": [],
          "approval": [],
          "rolls": "",
          "goto": "",
          "link": "21",
          "is_end": false,
          "node_type": "normal",
          "children": {
            "13": {
              "id": "13",
              "speaker": "Player",
              "text": "What news from the grove?",
              "context": "NodeContext: thoughtful. A potentially dire crisis was averted",
              "checkflags": [],
              "setflags": [],
              "ruletags": [],
              "approval": [],
              "rolls": "",
              "goto": "",
              "link": "21",
              "is_end": false,
              "node_type": "normal",
              "children": {
                "18": {
                  "id": "18",
                  "speaker": "Halsin",
                  "text": "The Shadow Druids. Their scheming was stopped, thanks to you... yet their malign ideals can find purchase and live on, even after the instigators themselves are vanquished.",
                  "context": "NodeContext: thoughtful. A potentially dire crisis was averted",
                  "checkflags": [
                    "DEN_ShadowDruid_Event_StartDenouncingScene"
                  ],
                  "setflags": [],
                  "ruletags": [],
                  "approval": [],
                  "rolls": "",
                  "goto": "",
                  "link": "21",
                  "is_end": false,
                  "node_type": "normal",
                  "children": {
                    "5": {
                      "id": "5",
                      "speaker": "Halsin",
                      "text": "Francesca has found some initiates still yearn for the false promises the Shadow Druids peddled. She has been working hard to show them the error of their ways.",
                      "context": "NodeContext: thoughtful. Perhaps thinking of his own perceived failings as archdruid",
                      "checkflags": [],
                      "setflags": [],
                      "ruletags": [],
                      "approval": [],
                      "rolls": "",
                      "goto": "",
                      "link": "",
                      "is_end": false,
                      "node_type": "normal",
                      "children": {
                        "21": {
                          "id": "21",
                          "speaker": "Halsin",
                          "text": "She is well-suited to the task - better than I, perhaps. To cleanse a land of shadows is one thing, but to sway a heart from a dark path is another matter entirely...",
                          "context": "NodeContext: thoughtful. Perhaps thinking of his own perceived failings as archdruid",
                          "checkflags": [],
                          "setflags": [],
                          "ruletags": [],
                          "approval": [],
                          "rolls": "",
                          "goto": "",
                          "link": "",
                          "is_end": false,
                          "node_type": "normal",
                          "children": {
                            "11": {
                              "id": "11",
                              "speaker": "",
                              "text": "",
                              "context": "",
                              "checkflags": [],
                              "setflags": [],
                              "ruletags": [],
                              "approval": [],
                              "rolls": "",
                              "goto": "3",
                              "link": "",
                              "is_end": false,
                              "node_type": "jump",
                              "children": {}
                            }
                          }
                        }
                      }
                    }
                  }
                },
                "1": {
                  "id": "1",
                  "speaker": "Halsin",
                  "text": "Wounds have healed, damage has been undone... balance has been restored. Those who seek to serve nature there can once again do so, with all their hearts.",
                  "context": "NodeContext: thoughtful",
                  "checkflags": [],
                  "setflags": [],
                  "ruletags": [],
                  "approval": [],
                  "rolls": "",
                  "goto": "",
                  "link": "21",
                  "is_end": false,
                  "node_type": "normal",
                  "children": {
                    "15": {
                      "id": "15",
                      "speaker": "Halsin",
                      "text": "There have been difficulties - some initiates harbour too much admiration for Kagha's course of action. Francesca will do what she must to rid them of such notions.",
                      "context": "",
                      "checkflags": [],
                      "setflags": [],
                      "ruletags": [],
                      "approval": [],
                      "rolls": "",
                      "goto": "",
                      "link": "21",
                      "is_end": false,
                      "node_type": "normal",
                      "children": {}
                    }
                  }
                }
              }
            },
            "2": {
              "id": "2",
              "speaker": "Player",
              "text": "Don't downplay your achievements. The shadow curse would still hold sway if not for you.",
              "context": "NodeContext: thoughtful",
              "checkflags": [],
              "setflags": [],
              "ruletags": [],
              "approval": [],
              "rolls": "",
              "goto": "",
              "link": "24",
              "is_end": false,
              "node_type": "normal",
              "children": {
                "22": {
                  "id": "22",
                  "speaker": "Halsin",
                  "text": "One grand victory may not be enough to absolve a host of small failures.",
                  "context": "NodeContext: thoughtful",
                  "checkflags": [],
                  "setflags": [],
                  "ruletags": [],
                  "approval": [],
                  "rolls": "",
                  "goto": "",
                  "link": "24",
                  "is_end": false,
                  "node_type": "normal",
                  "children": {
                    "20": {
                      "id": "20",
                      "speaker": "Halsin",
                      "text": "That is where true leadership lies - not in winning a single vast battle, but in fighting a thousand smaller ones. Making ten thousand difficult decisions. Finding balance, where none seems possible, day after day...",
                      "context": "NodeContext: speaking from experience.",
                      "checkflags": [],
                      "setflags": [],
                      "ruletags": [],
                      "approval": [],
                      "rolls": "",
                      "goto": "",
                      "link": "24",
                      "is_end": false,
                      "node_type": "normal",
                      "children": {
                        "3": {
                          "id": "3",
                          "speaker": "Halsin",
                          "text": "I was all too eager to surrender my responsibilities towards the grove. Perhaps I was never meant to be Archdruid - to be a leader.",
                          "context": "NodeContext: thoughtful. dwelling on his perceived failings as archdruid",
                          "checkflags": [
                            "DEN_Lockdown_State_Active = False"
                          ],
                          "setflags": [],
                          "ruletags": [],
                          "approval": [],
                          "rolls": "",
                          "goto": "",
                          "link": "24",
                          "is_end": false,
                          "node_type": "normal",
                          "children": {
                            "9": {
                              "id": "9",
                              "speaker": "Player",
                              "text": "You served the grove well, and found a worthy successor. No one can ask more of you.",
                              "context": "NodeContext: dreaming/ambitious",
                              "checkflags": [],
                              "setflags": [],
                              "ruletags": [],
                              "approval": [],
                              "rolls": "",
                              "goto": "",
                              "link": "24",
                              "is_end": false,
                              "node_type": "normal",
                              "children": {
                                "12": {
                                  "id": "12",
                                  "speaker": "Halsin",
                                  "text": "Still, though... I cannot help but wonder if there was more I could have done. Perhaps, Oak Father willing, I may yet have the chance some day...",
                                  "context": "NodeContext: dreaming/ambitious",
                                  "checkflags": [],
                                  "setflags": [],
                                  "ruletags": [],
                                  "approval": [],
                                  "rolls": "",
                                  "goto": "",
                                  "link": "",
                                  "is_end": false,
                                  "node_type": "normal",
                                  "children": {
                                    "24": {
                                      "id": "24",
                                      "speaker": "Halsin",
                                      "text": "Forgive me. The shadow curse occupied me so entirely and for so long... I almost miss the purpose it gave me. Now I must find a new one.",
                                      "context": "NodeContext: a little lost in thought",
                                      "checkflags": [],
                                      "setflags": [],
                                      "ruletags": [],
                                      "approval": [],
                                      "rolls": "",
                                      "goto": "",
                                      "link": "",
                                      "is_end": true,
                                      "node_type": "normal",
                                      "children": {}
                                    }
                                  }
                                }
                              }
                            },
                            "7": {
                              "id": "7",
                              "speaker": "Player",
                              "text": "Grove aside, I'm glad you stayed with me.",
                              "context": "NodeContext: Dreaming/ambitious. Wants to contribute",
                              "checkflags": [],
                              "setflags": [],
                              "ruletags": [],
                              "approval": [],
                              "rolls": "",
                              "goto": "",
                              "link": "24",
                              "is_end": false,
                              "node_type": "normal",
                              "children": {
                                "16": {
                                  "id": "16",
                                  "speaker": "Halsin",
                                  "text": "As am I. I can scarcely imagine life without your company now, and of course I made a promise to help you - one I intend to fulfil.",
                                  "context": "",
                                  "checkflags": [],
                                  "setflags": [],
                                  "ruletags": [],
                                  "approval": [
                                    "Halsin 1"
                                  ],
                                  "rolls": "",
                                  "goto": "",
                                  "link": "24",
                                  "is_end": false,
                                  "node_type": "normal",
                                  "children": {}
                                }
                              }
                            },
                            "4": {
                              "id": "4",
                              "speaker": "Player",
                              "text": "You could resume your position at the grove once we've defeated the Absolute.",
                              "context": "NodeContext: Dreaming/ambitious. Wants to contribute",
                              "checkflags": [],
                              "setflags": [],
                              "ruletags": [],
                              "approval": [],
                              "rolls": "",
                              "goto": "",
                              "link": "24",
                              "is_end": false,
                              "node_type": "normal",
                              "children": {
                                "19": {
                                  "id": "19",
                                  "speaker": "Halsin",
                                  "text": "I thought that would be the case once... yet perhaps the grove will not need me.",
                                  "context": "",
                                  "checkflags": [],
                                  "setflags": [],
                                  "ruletags": [],
                                  "approval": [],
                                  "rolls": "",
                                  "goto": "",
                                  "link": "24",
                                  "is_end": false,
                                  "node_type": "normal",
                                  "children": {}
                                }
                              }
                            },
                            "6": {
                              "id": "6",
                              "speaker": "Player",
                              "text": "Not everyone is meant for leadership. There's no shame in walking away.",
                              "context": "NodeContext: Dreaming/ambitious. Wants to contribute",
                              "checkflags": [],
                              "setflags": [],
                              "ruletags": [],
                              "approval": [],
                              "rolls": "",
                              "goto": "",
                              "link": "24",
                              "is_end": false,
                              "node_type": "normal",
                              "children": {
                                "23": {
                                  "id": "23",
                                  "speaker": "Halsin",
                                  "text": "Indeed. But I have roamed far and wide for years - whole lifetimes. I have seen much, done much, learned much. It would be a shame to not pass that on.",
                                  "context": "NodeContext: Dreaming/ambitious. Wants to contribute",
                                  "checkflags": [],
                                  "setflags": [],
                                  "ruletags": [],
                                  "approval": [],
                                  "rolls": "",
                                  "goto": "",
                                  "link": "24",
                                  "is_end": false,
                                  "node_type": "normal",
                                  "children": {}
                                }
                              }
                            }
                          }
                        },
                        "14": {
                          "id": "14",
                          "speaker": "Halsin",
                          "text": "I was all too eager to surrender my responsibilities towards the grove... and now it has been sealed away from the world. Perhaps I was never meant to be Archdruid - to be a leader.",
                          "context": "NodeContext: thoughtful. dwelling on his perceived failings as archdruid",
                          "checkflags": [
                            "DEN_Lockdown_State_Active"
